  <brief_title>PRG Combined With Autologous BMMSCs for Treatment of Diabetic Foot Ulcer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transplantation of Autologous Platelet Rich Gel Combined With Autologous Bone Marrow Mesenchymal Stem Cells for Treatment of Diabetic Foot Ulcer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
